{"tid":1198171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12朝4、5點，你會做啲咩呀？","createTime":"2019-06-10T07:07:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T07:37:41.000Z","uid":137789,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"516ccdfb31c264a2623d216f0aa7c31d4f077b83","tid":1198171,"uid":137789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:07:17.000Z","msg":"諗得到交通的話，大約4至5點最好，頂到啲人訓醒趕出嚟，人數真係好重要，游擊未受過訓練只係俾對家機會逐一剿滅<br />\n11號11點缺點:黑警可能會拉左好多人又消耗體力，消耗戰必敗，我地又人少。<br />\n12號缺點:會趕唔到<br />\n但我地可以11號4至5點，守4至5個鐘，等人支援<br />\n<br />\n照尋晚睇，今次好多係冇經歷3、5年前，而對家就好多係3、5年前老兵，有私怨，有決心，一鼓作氣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/iuM4xnONLpQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FiuM4xnONLpQ&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=7c252ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/iuM4xnONLpQ</a><br />\n個個衝出去死，之後仲有邊個？<br />\n唔衝嗰啲就係唔衝，衝嘅，一個都不能少，唔好作無謂嘅犧牲，要好小心每一個step<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n時、地、人，考慮時缺一不可，罷工就係製造時、人，民陣之類發起啲活動就係製造人、地，就住民陣之類啲活動嘅時間地點，靈活運用天時地利人和<br />\n自己衝？輸咗，做暴徒<br />\n夾到嘅，贏咗，都叫做返個烈士。<br />\n<br />\n你改變唔到民陣，各有各做，不如互相利用，你唔係尋晚衝完，佢今日有得聲淚俱下咁對住鏡頭攞分？佢拉到夠多人出嚟行，你都可以利用返個環境"},{"pid":"4978210437d8ac64729028dae8beb5fb8057f5f5","tid":1198171,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"push!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbb0bac14cd4e24fb007a6a2ee7fd8730202529","tid":1198171,"uid":205253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:14:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ea5a4dd52ef47cb27df3b6b841951177882fd7a4","tid":1198171,"uid":2544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:16:59.000Z","msg":"打錯11點 4， 5點呀"},{"pid":"cc23d302d16d269847dc948af348503ce49143e0","tid":1198171,"uid":2544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea5a4dd52ef47cb27df3b6b841951177882fd7a4","tid":1198171,"uid":2544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:16:59.000Z","msg":"打錯11點 4， 5點呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:17:26.000Z","msg":"*號"},{"pid":"47b944f20824a42609086c999532bac9e95bf1d5","tid":1198171,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"夜晚11點  你會做啲乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd48075fe5277113df04f780739c6fabddf16ca","tid":1198171,"uid":169261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:19:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3faf233e9a1a094b2fed40ccd92e6ebd4564c68e","tid":1198171,"uid":24284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T07:37:41.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}